\ \ \ \ \-d\ <arg>,\ \ \-\-identity\ <arg>
\ \ \ \ \ (required)\ \ Identity\ value

\ \ \ \ \-t\ <arg>,\ \ \-\-identity\-type\ <arg>
\ \ \ \ \ (required)\ \ Identity\ type

\ \ \ \ \-\-app\-key\ <file>
